room_title: Escape room "Voodoo" by Lockdown Escape Rooms in San Diego
room_description: A voodoo queen Arachne has the city trembling with fear. Her evil spells wreak havoc and destruction. The Mayor is desperate to stop her and has asked for your help. He can lure her in the office, but can only keep her for an hour. Will you find a way to break the spell?
